{"tid":1467723,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人 Be Water 更要 Be One。","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:30:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:33:40.000Z","uid":230879,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"55069814d9be9d1c2d5fbf82e469336a474d0451","tid":1467723,"uid":230879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:30:47.000Z","msg":"第一次開Po <br />\n並唔係有啲咩良計俾到大家，更唔係要屌人搞分化。<br />\n可能有人會屌我講廢話<br />\n但我只係希望香港人知一樣野，<br />\nBe water 更要 be one。<br />\n我地強大既並唔係我地既手法，手段，文宣<br />\n而個運動之所以強大係因為我地每個人既決心。<br />\n香港人，<br />\n不分化，<br />\n不割蓆，<br />\n不篤灰，<br />\nBe Water，<br />\nBe One。<br />\n<br />\n我地香港人是打不死的。"},{"pid":"b7995b5cc37230803b7d0098a101526abe8b2ef9","tid":1467723,"uid":230879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:33:40.000Z","msg":"自推"}]}